OL,3,CWhy are energy bills going up and how
OL,4,Ccan you save money?
OL,6,FLowering the flow temperature of your
OL,7,Fboiler can be a quick way to save #65.
OL,9,FMany people have the flow set at 70C,
OL,10,Fjust turning it down to between 55-
OL,11,F 60C can use 6% less energy, and you
OL,12,Fusually don't notice the difference.
OL,14,FSo, a call to action, it's a good time
OL,15,Fto look at how you pay - as well as
OL,16,Fwho you pay - and what you pay.
